All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AbstractTaskLog
The AbstractTaskLog class is an abstract class representing a log of tasks.
AllTasksLog
The AllTasksLog class represents one of the two possible types of task logs, All Tasks.
CategoryLog
The CategoryLog class represents one of the two possible types of task logs, a category log.
ILogList<E>
Interface for logged items.
ISortedList<E extends Comparable<E>>
Interface for a list that keeps objects in sorted order as defined by the Comparable interface.
LogList<E>
The LogList class implements the ILogList interface with functionality for an array list.
Project
The Project class handles a project in the WolfTracker system.
ProjectReader
The ProjectReader class handles the reading and processing of project files.
ProjectWriter
The ProjectWriter class handles writing projects and summary statistics to files.
SortedList<E extends Comparable<E>>
The SortedList class implements the ISortedList interface.
Task
The Task class handles a task in the WolfTracker system.
WolfTrackerGUI
Container for the Wolf Tracker project that provides the user the ability to interact with projects and logged tasks.
